## Stage 1: Keyword Research
Brave Search + Claude generates 25 long-tail keywords from seed keyword.
Trigger: { "status": "keyword_research", "seed_keyword": "...", "brand_id": "rec..." }

## Stage 2: SERP Analysis (Core)
Scrapes top 5 ranking pages. Claude extracts NLP terms, heading structure, PAA questions.
Trigger: { "status": "serp_analysis", "keyword_id": "rec..." }

## Stage 3: Write Article
Claude agents write article section-by-section using SERP brief. Checks NLP term coverage.
Trigger: { "status": "write_article", "keyword_id": "rec..." }

## Stage 4: Publish to Sanity
Pushes article to Sanity CMS. Updates Airtable status.
Trigger: { "status": "publish_article", "article_id": "rec..." }
